hing about it. There are so many bad things about it that it just feels like a fever dream. Can anyone who\u2019s watched or read Umbre\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/persona-3-reload-live-action-ad-umbrella-academy-aidan-1851186469\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/persona-3-reload-live-action-ad-umbrella-academy-aidan-1851186469", "date_published": "2024-01-22T21:15:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": null, "album": "", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/a6d5ae57a1a390d5c967f40dcf56567c.png", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "Suicide Squad\u2019s First New Playable Character Will Be The Joker", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/22114bc705fdce5f9dde9961f13e8a48.jpg\" /><p>Rocksteady has revealed some of its post-launch plans for <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/suicide-squad-justice-league-trailer-offline-mode-1851083286\">Suicide Squad: Kill The Justice League</a>. The biggest piece of news is that the Joker will be the first new playable character added to Suicide Squad post-launch. And no, this isn\u2019t the Joker from the Arkham games. <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/the-joker-dies-in-the-first-act-of-arkham-city-or-does-5845285\">He\u2019s still dead</a>. Instead, this is a new Joker\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/suicide-squad-joker-first-season-free-content-dlc-march-1851186411\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/suicide-squad-joker-first-season-free-content-dlc-march-1851186411", "date_published": "2024-01-22T21:00:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": null, "album": "", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/22114bc705fdce5f9dde9961f13e8a48.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "The Week In Games: Brawling Bears, Soulful Gangsters, And More New Releases", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/256d0a626eb976c22cea4244877daf34.jpg\" /><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/january-games-this-week-tekken-8-like-a-dragon-howl-1851185888\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/january-games-this-week-tekken-8-like-a-dragon-howl-1851185888", "date_published": "2024-01-22T19:45:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": null, "album": "", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/256d0a626eb976c22cea4244877daf34.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "As The Servers Shut Down, The Day Before Is No More", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/f5c2bdfdde57b877c96bd8ef0987911c.jpg\" /><p>Controversial, PC-only shooter The Day Before is officially dead, barely a month and a half after its launch. <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/day-before-steam-zombie-reviews-survival-horror-1851082164\">Steam\u2019s much-hyped zombie game</a>, which saw developer Fntastic shutter its doors almost immediately after release, is now totally unplayable. For a few weeks following its disastrous debut, it existed in a state\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/the-day-before-fntastic-mytona-steam-dead-game-1851185900\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/the-day-before-fntastic-mytona-steam-dead-game-1851185900", "date_published": "2024-01-22T19:30:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": null, "album": "", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/f5c2bdfdde57b877c96bd8ef0987911c.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "After Playing Palworld For 6 Hours I Still Haven't Shot A Pok\u00e9mon With A Gun", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/174b42e1e2e9b6df6cafac32719fe907.jpg\" /><p>Over the weekend, I downloaded <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/palworld-pokemon-guns-mod-pikachu-ash-1851184776\">Palworld</a> on my PC. I was excited. After all the weird trailers and screenshots showing Pok\u00e9mon-like creatures using assault rifles or being shot with handguns, I was ready to earn official Xbox achievements as I killed Pok\u00e9mon facsimiles using modern guns. It was hunting time. And then,\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/palworld-shoot-pokemon-with-guns-impressions-review-pc-1851185681\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/palworld-shoot-pokemon-with-guns-impressions-review-pc-1851185681", "date_published": "2024-01-22T18:30:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": null, "album": "", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/174b42e1e2e9b6df6cafac32719fe907.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "CD Projekt Red Is Ramping Up For The Witcher 4, Investigating AI", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6a86d5519cf61e6e1256558636b67aa3.jpg\" /><p>The Witcher 4 hasn\u2019t entered the production stage at CD Projekt Red yet, but the developer is getting ready to start work on the highly anticipated follow-up to 2015\u2019s Witcher 3. By the middle of 2024, the Polish studio hopes to have 400 people working on the game. And according to new co-CEO Adam Badowski, not a\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/witcher-4-cyberpunk-2-cd-project-ai-1851185524\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/witcher-4-cyberpunk-2-cd-project-ai-1851185524", "date_published": "2024-01-22T18:00:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": null, "album": "", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6a86d5519cf61e6e1256558636b67aa3.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "New Deal Offers 8 Great Shooters For Just $10", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/cae48ae3c81bcd07e4ad577aecae6380.jpg\" /><p>A new deal letting you create your own bundle of shooters, with options that include new classics like Dusk or <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/doom-weirdest-ports-keyboard-atm-calculator-tractor-pc-1850726374\">older hits like Doom</a>, is the best way to instantly fill your Steam library with some of the best FPS games ever made for just $10 or less.<br /></p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/new-deal-fps-shooters-steam-pc-doom-quake-dusk-1851185295\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/new-deal-fps-shooters-steam-pc-doom-quake-dusk-1851185295", "date_published": "2024-01-22T17:15:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": null, "album": "", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/cae48ae3c81bcd07e4ad577aecae6380.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "British Army Planned To Use Fortnite In Recruitment Campaign [Update]", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6088aa7bc4e6b3a44e73018cf0664311.jpg\" /><p>Join us in trying to think of something more gross than a nation\u2019s army using a children\u2019s video game as a recruitment tool. That was the plan of the British Army, who thought it might be rather jolly to recruit some influencers to play Fortnite, to promote joining their ranks. However, it looks like they\u2019ve since\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/fortnite-epic-british-army-elzthewitch-yungfilly1-1851184946\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/fortnite-epic-british-army-elzthewitch-yungfilly1-1851184946", "date_published": "2024-01-22T16:15:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": null, "album": "", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6088aa7bc4e6b3a44e73018cf0664311.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "Palworld Devs Aren\u2019t Worried About A Nintendo Lawsuit", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/911bf10525d54114d1391d480977fd1a.jpg\" /><p>We\u2019re about done with the first month of the year, and 2024\u2019s biggest game is already here in the form of <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/palworld-is-what-happens-when-you-mix-pokemon-and-capit-1848412903\">Palworld</a>. The colloquially named \u201c<a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/pokemon-with-guns-palworld-scam-real-steam-release-xbox-1851173423\">Pok\u00e9mon with guns</a>\u201d open-world survival crafting title is dominating both Steam and Twitch in spite of the controversy it\u2019s courted, particularly around similarities in monster\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/palworld-pokemon-lawsuit-pocketpair-nintendo-pc-xbox-1851184907\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/palworld-pokemon-lawsuit-pocketpair-nintendo-pc-xbox-1851184907", "date_published": "2024-01-22T16:00:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": null, "album": "", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/911bf10525d54114d1391d480977fd1a.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "Modders Have Already Put Actual Pok\u00e9mon In Palworld", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/fab90231e350cee45ffb40042c6e29aa.jpg\" /><p>Even before it entered Early Access on January 19, Pocketpair\u2019s monster-collecting survival game Palworld was widely being referred to as \u201cPok\u00e9mon With Guns.\u201d But mere days after launch, modders have already taken steps to really drive the comparison home by adding actual Pok\u00e9mon characters to the mix.<br /></p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/palworld-pokemon-guns-mod-pikachu-ash-1851184776\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/palworld-pokemon-guns-mod-pikachu-ash-1851184776", "date_published": "2024-01-22T15:25:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": null, "album": "", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/fab90231e350cee45ffb40042c6e29aa.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "Eight Years Later, Final Fantasy's Best Ending Still Hits Hard", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/82ba8bc725246ff72fe1aedb338ef3a2.jpg\" /><p>Brotherhood is a theme so overt in <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-xv-the-kotaku-review-1789400066\">Final Fantasy XV</a> that it\u2019s the title of the game\u2019s <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://www.kotaku.com.au/2016/03/final-fantasy-xv-gets-a-five-episode-anime-prequel/\">five-episode prequel anime</a>. An outlier in a series that usually leverages expansive and diverse casts, FF15 instead focuses entirely on a road trip with four lads. Tehy spend most of their time cruising around in a convertible,\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-best-ending-ff15-ffxv-1851180289\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-best-ending-ff15-ffxv-1851180289", "date_published": "2024-01-22T14:15:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": null, "album": "", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/82ba8bc725246ff72fe1aedb338ef3a2.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}]